{"tid":169031,"cid":7,"subCid":0,"title":"達明一派開騷暗諷操控選舉洗腦教育","createTime":"2017-03-24T02:52:37.000Z","updateTime":"2017-03-24T15:52:46.000Z","uid":25558,"like":1,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"633a749c4abc66f5a94c9888fc50064d942d6a0e","tid":169031,"uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-24T02:52:37.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"http://hkm.appledaily.com/detail.php?guid=19968049&amp;category_guid=462&amp;category=daily&amp;issue=20170324\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhkm.appledaily.com%2Fdetail.php%3Fguid%3D19968049%26category_guid%3D462%26category%3Ddaily%26issue%3D20170324&d=AnzAvEp6rraOVT5%2FQxAiQS7bS0i5kAixZS1hjGmvpwM%3D&h=b239f7e0\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhkm.appledaily.com%2Fdetail.php%3Fguid%3D19968049%26category_guid%3D462%26category%3Ddaily%26issue%3D20170324&h=107f3a60\" target=\"_blank\">http://hkm.appledaily.com/detail.php?guid=19968049&amp;category_guid=462&amp;category=daily&amp;issue=20170324</a><br />\n<br />\n達明一派開騷<br />\n暗諷操控選舉洗腦教育<br />\n<br />\n娛樂要聞&nbsp;<br />\n<br />\n&nbsp;<br />\n<br />\n￼&nbsp;￼&nbsp;￼&nbsp;￼&nbsp;￼<br />\n<br />\n黃耀明與劉以達相隔五年再度合體，昨晚假紅館舉行「達明卅一派對」演唱會，慶祝入行31年。因政治取向被封殺的明哥沒有贊助商、海報「被下架」，於演唱會論盡社會敏感議題，包括操控選舉及洗腦教育等，仍獲不少內地歌迷專程來港撐場。<br />\n<br />\n￼<br />\n<br />\n【扮紅衞兵】<br />\n達明一派昨晚在紅館舉行頭場演唱會，黃耀明（右二）與劉以達扮紅衞兵出場。<br />\n<img src=\"http://static.apple.appledaily.com.hk/images/apple-photos/apple/20170324/large/24ec1p1.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fstatic.apple.appledaily.com.hk%2Fimages%2Fapple-photos%2Fapple%2F20170324%2Flarge%2F24ec1p1.jpg&h=1b210833&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n首個沒有贊助商的紅館演唱會「達明卅一派對」昨晚在紅館開鑼，一連三場騷由環球唱片一力承擔製作費，舞台簡約，只是一個長形台，再加一個大銀幕，入場觀眾有七至八成，捧場的圈中人有鍾楚紅、俞琤、盧凱彤、黃偉文及林夕等。<br />\n<br />\n【抱着希望】<br />\n<img src=\"http://static.apple.appledaily.com.hk/images/apple-photos/apple/20170324/large/24ec1p11.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fstatic.apple.appledaily.com.hk%2Fimages%2Fapple-photos%2Fapple%2F20170324%2Flarge%2F24ec1p11.jpg&h=c57f2744&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n【嘲諷洗腦】<br />\n[img]<a href=\"http://static.apple.appledaily.com.hk/images/apple-photos/apple/20170324/large/24ec1p2.jpg\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fstatic.apple.appledaily.com.hk%2Fimages%2Fapple-photos%2Fapple%2F20170324%2Flarge%2F24ec1p2.jpg&d=AnzAvEp6rraOVT5%2FQxAiQS7bS0i5kAixZS1hjGmvpwM%3D&h=7d058713\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://static.apple.appledaily.com.hk/images/apple-photos/apple/20170324/large/24ec1p2.jpg</a><br />\n[/img]"},{"pid":"1522925d6b5ea724f4cd911249d71a33da7e0871","tid":169031,"uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-24T02:57:31.000Z","msg":"扮紅衞兵登場<br />\n<br />\n一如所料，達明演唱會滲入不少政治及社會議題，黃耀明及劉以達於8時55分出場，與約30位樂隊成員穿上如紅衞兵軍服唱《四季交易會》。演唱會又以「監控」、「洗腦」、「情慾」及「失敗/宿命」分四部份，當達明獻唱《崩裂》時，銀幕打出「戰爭即和平」、「即力量」等字眼，觀眾隨即歡呼。<br />\n到「洗腦」部份，達明唱《1+4=14》時，大銀幕用紅色字打出2017、689、64等數字，唱《填充》一曲則打出「真理部：家庭破碎，造成槍擊重案」，然後唱《甜美生活》，舞蹈員則扮學生坐着，諷刺香港出現洗腦式教育。<br />\n<br />\n￼ <img src=\"http://static.apple.appledaily.com.hk/images/apple-photos/apple/20170324/large/24ec1p10.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fstatic.apple.appledaily.com.hk%2Fimages%2Fapple-photos%2Fapple%2F20170324%2Flarge%2F24ec1p10.jpg&h=09d527da&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n【何詩撐場】<br />\n唯一嘉賓何韻詩與達明合唱《下落不明》。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n￼ <img src=\"http://static.apple.appledaily.com.hk/images/apple-photos/apple/20170324/large/24ec1p5.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fstatic.apple.appledaily.com.hk%2Fimages%2Fapple-photos%2Fapple%2F20170324%2Flarge%2F24ec1p5.jpg&h=9f6b06c9&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n【戀愛有罪】<br />\n明哥唱《禁色》時，分別有一對男女、男男擁抱又分開，寓意異性及同性的苦戀。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n￼<br />\n<img src=\"http://static.apple.appledaily.com.hk/images/apple-photos/apple/20170324/large/24ec1p4.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fstatic.apple.appledaily.com.hk%2Fimages%2Fapple-photos%2Fapple%2F20170324%2Flarge%2F24ec1p4.jpg&h=53c10657&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n【充滿反思】<br />\n演唱會充滿着反思，一個「party」驅逐另一個「party」，共和國才誕生。"},{"pid":"d1bf512cd5f88de2c1178dcca3d10161a582d74e","tid":169031,"uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-24T03:00:31.000Z","msg":"播出佔領地方<br />\n<br />\n雖然昨晚達明沒有唱《撐起雨傘》，只播出前奏音樂，但銀幕播放曾被佔領的地方，包括龍和道、銅鑼灣崇光對出路面、旺角及政總等地方，唱《十個救火的少年》觀眾最high，全場站立伴唱。演唱會過了三分二，明哥首度開腔說：「多謝，我以為呢部份會好傷感，呢部份好矛盾！」阿達則問觀眾：「你哋high唔high呀？」而演唱會唯一嘉賓何韻詩則於達明唱《下落不明》時現身。<br />\n採訪：盧妹<br />\n攝影：沈健程<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n演唱會曲目<br />\n<br />\n【1】《四季交易會》<br />\n【2】《我有兩個》<br />\n【3】《你望我望》<br />\n【4】《後窗》<br />\n【5】《崩裂》<br />\n【6】《1+4=14》<br />\n【7】《填充》<br />\n【8】《甜美生活》<br />\n【9】《每日一禁果》<br />\n【10】《青春殘酷物語》<br />\n【11】《迷戀》<br />\n【12】《暗湧》<br />\n【13】《愛在瘟疫蔓延時》<br />\n【14】《禁色》<br />\n【15】《天問》<br />\n【16】《撐起雨傘》前奏、《馬路天使》<br />\n【17】《迷惘夜車》<br />\n【18】《今夜星光燦爛》<br />\n【19】《十個救火的少年》<br />\n【20】《今天應該很高興》<br />\n【21】《下落不明》（與何韻詩合唱）<br />\n【22】《Under Pressure》（與何韻詩合唱）<br />\n【23】《剎那天地》<br />\n【24】《排名不分先後左右忠奸》<br />\n【25】《It's My Party》<br />\n【26】《溜冰滾族》<br />\n【27】《繼續追尋》<br />\n【28】《Heroes》<br />\n【29】《末世情》<br />\n【30】《石頭記》<br />\n【31】《晚節不保》<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n相關新聞<br />\n<br />\n￼<br />\n<br />\n歌迷搶紀念品　唱片最貴1750元<br />\n<br />\n娛樂要聞&nbsp;4小時前<br />\n<br />\n￼<br />\n<br />\n達明內地歌迷：想有發聲機會<br />\n<br />\n娛樂要聞&nbsp;4小時前"},{"pid":"2d6f8815bc887c35cd9c10fec2a909bd8b6c2eb0","tid":169031,"uid":34676,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-24T03:14:23.000Z","msg":"開始覺得好撚煩"},{"pid":"2f79353c88475b3f86f8dfe183761e7d4cb1de66","tid":169031,"uid":40662,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-24T03:34:13.000Z","msg":"竟然冇唱天花亂墜"},{"pid":"1e247f580c40943db70996fb6658ff1bfe3dc77a","tid":169031,"uid":18725,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-24T15:48:56.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>竟然冇唱天花亂墜</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n今晚有天花亂墜做ending，但無末世情"},{"pid":"16bb041a620513eb71e0d895e94733c323b5daf1","tid":169031,"uid":53498,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-24T15:52:46.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}